name: Delivery Much
description:
Are you ready for the best delivery game ever?
Watch out for the platform colors, shoot them timely, fit them perfectly.
Create continuous lanes, deliver more packages, earn multiplied points.
Unlock special items, customize your crew, deliver different packages, show your unique dance figures.
Don’t forget! You can join new carriers on the way. So, no worries about the Fallen!
